snippet.title: Pink Helps Fan With Terminal Cancer’s Dream Come True
snippet.description:
Pink fulfills the dreams of a terminally-ill fan named Diana Berberian by sitting down for a heartwarming 30-minute Zoom call.
#Pink #P!nk
